  Philosopher 1: EATING
  Philosopher 2: Hungry
  Philosopher 3: Thinking
  Philosopher 4: Waiting(left)
Chopstick states:
  Chopstick 0: Available
  Chopstick 1: Held by 1
  Chopstick 2: Held by 1
  Chopstick 3: Available
  Chopstick 4: Held by 4
System healthy
====================================
...
=== Simulation Complete ===
*)
